    "date": "2022-07-13T12:34:57Z",
    "text": "Smart Intersections Act of 2021\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Transportation to award grants for improving the functioning of traffic signals through active management of traffic signal operations. State, tribal, and local government entities are eligible for these grants.\n\nAdditionally, the Government Accountability Office must study the potential for reducing greenhouse gas emissions by improving the efficiency of traffic systems."
